evidence.text: Notice of Voluntary Dismissal ... dismisses this case without prejudice, pursuant to Rule 41, because Defendant has changed its certification requirements since the filing of this suit. The motion for a preliminary injunction filed on March 21, 2025 (ECF No. 5), is accordingly withdrawn.
